• Biloxi Personal Injury Attorney Working for You
    Biloxi injury attorney Corban Gunn has been helping people like you recover compensation and recover from their injuries in Mississippi car and truck accidents, work accidents and more for over ten years.
  • BILOXI ATTORNEY HELPING INJURED EMPLOYEES OBTAIN MISSISSIPPI WORKERS’ COMPENSATION BENEFITS
    Corban Gunn, Attorney at Law, is a full-service Biloxi law firm helping victims of personal injury or wrongful death and their families across Mississippi recover compensation for their injuries.
  • BILOXI CRIMINAL DEFENSE ATTORNEY
    Corban Gunn provides strong, aggressive criminal defense representation to persons charged with criminal felony matters in Mississippi state and federal courts
  • A BILOXI CAR ACCIDENT ATTORNEY CAN HELP YOU RECOVER COMPENSATION WHEN YOU ARE HURT
    Corban Gunn works to hold negligent drivers responsible for the harm they have caused and help accident victims and their families deal with the financial and emotional loss they have suffered due to another’s negligence or reckless driving.
  • EXPERIENCED BILOXI DUI ATTORNEY
    Let our experience work for you. Please call our office today to schedule a consultation. The initial visit is free, and you do not owe us anything unless we take your case.

description:
At the Biloxi law office of Corban Gunn, Attorney at Law, we take pride in combining honest, straightforward counsel with personal attention and high-quality client service. We offer personal injury and criminal defense representation to individuals and families near the Gulf Coast and across Mississippi. 

Let us provide the results-oriented advocacy you deserve if you have been injured by someone else's negligence...
